ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It is a good course to help you learn more about the science field, including funding apllication and so forth.
Important ethics course. Yes I would recommend it.

comments: Introduced us to various ethical issues that we could encounter in grad school
